      "capture_text": "The paper reports a thermal-mismatch dislocation-density model for TiB/Ti-6Al-4V: rho = 6*abs(delta_alpha)*delta_T*Vf/((1-Vf)*b*d), followed by delta_sigma = alpha*G*b*sqrt(rho). The bound calculation uses matrix E=112.3 GPa and nu=0.34 (G=41.903 GPa), TiB and Ti-6Al-4V CTE values 5.9e-6 and 9.0e-6 K^-1, delta_T=900 K, b=0.295 nm, mean reinforcement diameter 5 micrometres, alpha=1, and Vf=0.02, 0.035, 0.05. These are model estimates, not direct dislocation-density measurements.",
